pendingApplications.proposal:
Demolition of the curtilage listed Gun Shop and Long Shed buildings and internal and external repairs and alterations to the Grade II* listed Whist House including:
• full roof and external tile hanging renewal;
• replacement of concrete floors and dilapidated timber floor areas at ground floor level with breathable limecrete, and the addition of a pamment floor and associated modifications to historic stair and panelling;
• removal of failing render and the repair/restoration of brickwork, plinths and quoins;
• repair and renewal of failed lath and plaster walls and ceilings;
• joinery repairs and modifications as scheduled including upgrading and replacement of doors and windows;
• alterations to internal openings, partitions and the addition of glazed screens;
• new tile hung and glazed lift addition to south elevation with 4 no. new associated new openings;
• demolitions of west garden walls;
• removal of modern external slabs and new brick plinths to existing columns where ground level reduced.
